OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779793371
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in 'self defence' as
OL,4,CTrump says talks 'proceeding nicely'
OL,6,FThe US says it has carried out "self-
OL,7,Fdefence" strikes on Iran, despite
OL,8,FDonald Trump stating that negotiations
OL,9,Fbetween the two nations are
OL,10,F"proceeding nicely".
OL,12,FThe strikes on Monday were targeting
OL,13,Fmissile launch sites and boats placing
OL,14,Fmines to "protect our troops from
OL,15,Fthreats posed by Iranian forces", said
OL,16,FCaptain Tim Hawkins, the spokesman for
OL,17,FUS Central Command.
OL,19,FThe US continues to "defend our forces
OL,20,Fwhile using restraint during the
OL,21,Fongoing ceasefire", Hawkins added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
