OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in 'self defence' as
OL,4,CTrump says talks 'proceeding nicely'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIran's regime has not officially
OL,12,Fissued a response to the strikes, with
OL,13,Fparliament speaker Mohammad Bagher
OL,14,FQalibaf returning to Tehran from Qatar
OL,15,Fon Monday evening following
OL,16,Fnegotiations over the possible deal
OL,17,Fwith the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
