OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779793371
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in 'self defence' as
OL,4,CTrump says talks 'proceeding nicely'
OL,6,FNews website Tabnak, believed to be
OL,7,Fclose to former Revolutionary Guard
OL,8,Fchief Mohsen Rezaei, said four dead
OL,9,FGuard troops had been killed in
OL,10,FAmerican strikes on boats.
OL,12,FIranian state television separately
OL,13,Falso reported blasts around Bandar
OL,14,FAbbas, a city on the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,15,Fhome to a military port and a dual-use
OL,16,Fairport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
