OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779793371
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in 'self defence' as
OL,4,CTrump says talks 'proceeding nicely'
OL,6,FUS President Trump said over the
OL,7,Fweekend a US-Iran deal had been
OL,8,F"largely negotiated" but warned that
OL,9,Frelations could go "back to the
OL,10,Fbattlefront" if no agreement were made.
OL,12,FHe wrote on Truth Social:
OL,13,F"Negotiations with the Islamic
OL,14,FRepublic of Iran are proceeding
OL,15,Fnicely! It will only be a Great Deal
OL,16,Ffor all or, no Deal at all ` Back to
OL,17,Fthe Battlefront and shooting, but
OL,18,Fbigger and stronger than ever before `
OL,19,FAnd nobody wants that!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779793371
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in 'self defence' as
OL,4,CTrump says talks 'proceeding nicely'
OL,6,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio said
OL,7,Ffollowing the strikes that a US-Iran
OL,8,Fdeal is still on the table as he met
OL,9,Fwith foreign ministers from Australia,
OL,10,FIndia and Japan in New Delhi on
OL,11,FTuesday.
OL,13,F"We'll see if we can make progress. I
OL,14,Fthink it's a lot of talking back and
OL,15,Fforth going on about specific language
OL,16,Fin the initial document, so it'll take
OL,17,Fa few days," Rubio told reporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
