OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779793371
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in 'self defence' as
OL,4,CTrump says talks 'proceeding nicely'
OL,6,FEarlier, Trump said any agreement to
OL,7,Fend the Iran war should include a
OL,8,Frequirement for several additional
OL,9,Fcountries, including Saudi Arabia,
OL,10,FQatar and Pakistan, to join the
OL,11,FAbraham Accords, the US-brokered
OL,12,Fagreements aimed at normalising
OL,13,Frelations with Israel.
OL,15,FBahrain and the United Arab Emirates
OL,16,Fbecame the first Arab countries to
OL,17,Fjoin in 2020, diplomatically
OL,18,Frecognising Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
