PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779793371
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in 'self defence' as
OL,4,CTrump says talks 'proceeding nicely'
OL,6,FTrump stated that "after all the work"
OL,7,Fdone by the US "to try and pull this
OL,8,Fvery complex puzzle together", it
OL,9,Fshould be mandatory that the countries
OL,10,F"simultaneously" sign onto the Abraham
OL,11,FAccords.
OL,13,F"If they don't, they should not be
OL,14,Fpart of this deal in that it shows bad
OL,15,Fintention," Trump wrote on Truth
OL,16,FSocial on Monday.
OL,26,@nD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
