OL,3,CUS strikes Iran in 'self defence' as
OL,4,CTrump says talks 'proceeding nicely'
OL,6,FSaudi Arabia, in particular, has for
OL,7,Fdecades called on Israel to return to
OL,8,Fits 1967 borders and allow the
OL,9,Fformation of a Palestinian nation with
OL,10,FEast Jerusalem as its capital.
OL,12,FIsrael's conduct in the war against
OL,13,FHamas in Gaza has also alienated Gulf
OL,14,FArab states and the wider Muslim world
OL,15,Fas well.
OL,17,FEgypt, Jordan and Turkey, also
OL,18,Fmentioned by Trump, have diplomatic
OL,19,Frelations with Israel already, but
OL,20,Fthese have been strained since the
OL,21,Fstart of the Gaza war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
